query: SELECT e.id, e.title, e.coupleName1, e.coupleName2, COUNT(g.id) as guest_count FROM events e LEFT JOIN guests g ON e.id = g.eventId GROUP BY e.id ORDER BY guest_count DESC LIMIT 5;
